people like us ( known during production as welcome to people ) is a 2012 american drama film directed by alex kurtzman in his directorial debut . the film was written by kurtzman , roberto orci and jody lambert , and stars chris pine , elizabeth banks , olivia wilde , michael hall &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and michelle pfeiffer . a. r. rahman composed the soundtrack . the film was released by touchstone pictures on june 29 , 2012 .